    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1931-12-23T12:00:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1931-12-23T12:00:00-05:00" n="267"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d267">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">462.00296A/86: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Consul at Basel</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Cochran</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Basel</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1931-12-23T18:00:00+01:00"
                            >December 23, 1931—6 p.m.</date>
                        <lb/>[Received December 23—12:50 p.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>For Castle. Final agreement on report reached this afternoon. Signing will take
                    place at 8:30 tonight. Press summary will be given out but the text will not be
                    issued for several hours. Since these will both be telegraphed by the Associated
                    Press, I shall not cable but mail text.<note n="51a" xml:id="d267fn51a">For
                        text, see Great Britain, Cmd. 3995, Germany No. 1 (1932): <hi rend="italic"
                            >Report of the Special Advisory Committee convened under the Agreement
                            with Germany concluded at The Hague on January 20, 1930</hi>, Basle,
                        December 23, 1931.</note>
                </p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Cochran</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
